Phase 3a — catalog/solutions consolidation (done, verified):
- api-mock.ts: deleted serverState.catalog (the disconnected 2-SKU
  stub with ids like sku-seed-1/sku-seed-2 that never matched the
  real 38-SKU catalog). MockCatalogApi's get/add/update/delete are
  now stateless pass-throughs -- confirmed via grep that nothing in
  the UI reads GET /api/catalog's response, so there is nothing to
  keep in sync. This is the direct fix for the CatalogManager
  price-rollback bug: updateCatalogSku() can no longer throw SKU
